name: Nyai Rantam Sari
shortLoreBlurb: Nyai Rantam Sari is a spirit from Java/Indonesia linked to sea consort, wealth. Offerings seek calm waters and life-giving rains.
overlapsLinks: Caishen (Chinese), Fortuna (Roman), Lakshmi (Hindu), Naga (India/SE Asia), Poseidon (Greek), Tangaroa (Polynesia), Yemaya (Yoruba)
